Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:30.34,1080P-sgsm-50,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4\move(-20,10,10,10,0,500)}阿6已经鸽子到2022年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.52,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hello it's Scott Manley here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.52,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你好 我是Scott Manley
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:09.20,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's a day past Christmas and I missed a very important birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:09.20,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是一个圣诞节之后的一天 而我错过了一个非常重要的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:13.71,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}the 40th anniversary of the first launch of the Ariane rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:13.71,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就是阿丽亚娜火箭首飞40周年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:19.29,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Yes back on ChristmasEve 1979 Europe launched the Ariane 1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:19.29,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 早在1979年圣诞节前夕 欧洲就发射了阿丽亚娜1号火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:23.70,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but Europe's space launch ambitions started decades earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:23.70,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但欧洲航天发射的雄心早在几十年前就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:28.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Much more politics was involved since it was an international organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:28.31,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}由于这是一个国际组织 所以涉及的政治因素更多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:32.38,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The Europa launcher was originally planned in 1962
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:32.38,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欧罗巴号运载火箭最初计划于1962年发射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:37.35,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and it was led by the UK with France and Germany as main collaborators.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:37.35,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并由英国牵头 而法国和德国为主要合作者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:41.89,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The UK had developed a missile called the Blue Streak but it had never deployed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:41.89,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}英国曾研制出一种名为蓝纹的导弹 但从未部署过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:45.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They had proposed this as the first stage for the Europa rocket
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:45.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们曾建议将其作为欧罗巴火箭的一级
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:49.69,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}with the French building the second stage and Germany building the third stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:49.69,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}法国负责二级的制造 德国负责三级的制造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.37,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This made integration problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.37,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这使得整合出现了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:55.07,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ultimately it didn't fly particularly well
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:55.07,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最终 它并没有飞得特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:59.98,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and Britain pulled out the project in 1968 to develop their own Black Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:59.98,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而英国在1968年退出了这个项目 发展自己的黑箭火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:06.15,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Germany pulled out in 1972 and the program officially stopped in 1973.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:06.15,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}德国在1972年退出 该项目在1973年正式停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:12.00,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So in the meantime the British black arrow project successfully launched hardware into orbit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:12.00,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以在这期间 英国的黑箭项目成功地将设备发射到了轨道上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:14.23,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and then promptly stopped doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:14.23,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后马上就不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:21.02,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The French developed the Diamant rocket which was able to launch about a dozen times with nine successes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:21.02,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}法国人研制的钻石火箭 发了十几次 其中九次成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:25.26,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But it was only able to put about 160 kilograms into low earth orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:25.26,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但它只能把160公斤左右的重量送入近地轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:29.36,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And so Ariane started out as a project called L3S
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:29.36,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以阿丽亚娜一开始的项目叫L3S
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:35.47,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}with the goal of designing a rocket that would be able to launch 800 kilograms to geostationary orbit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:35.47,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}目标是设计一种能够将800公斤的载荷发射到地球静止轨道(GEO)的火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:36.43,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and this is significant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:36.43,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而这是相当可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:41.46,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}because Ariane I believe is the only rocket that has been designed from the start
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:41.46,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为我相信阿丽亚娜是唯一的 从一开始就这样设计的火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:46.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}with the intention of launching payloads to geostationary orbit rather than low earth orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:46.90,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其设计目的就是将有效载荷发射到地球静止轨道而不是近地轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The name Ariane comes from Greek mythology.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.86,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜这个名字来自希腊神话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:52.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}In english we know her as Ariadne.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:52.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在英语中 我们知道她是阿里阿德涅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:54.27,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}She gave Theseus the thread
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:54.27,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她给了忒修斯一条线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:58.40,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}that he used to find his way out of the labyrinth after defeating the minotaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:58.40,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在打败牛头人后 他用它找到了走出迷宫的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}In French she was known as Ariane.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.86,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在法国 她被称为阿丽亚娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:06.38,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ariane was very much led by the French with 60 percent of the funding coming from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:06.38,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜是由法国人牵头的 60%的资金来自法国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.87,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}20 percent of the funding came from Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.87,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}20%的资金来自德国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:13.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and most of the other European nations contributed a few percent to the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:13.94,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而大多数其他欧洲国家为该项目贡献了百分之几的资金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.81,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The design of the Ariane would borrow from work already done on the Europa booster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.81,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜的设计将使用欧罗巴助推器上已经完成的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.97,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}After Britain left they sought a replacement first stage booster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.97,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在英国离开后 他们在寻求一级助推器的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:27.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and they came up with a stage that had four Viking engines
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:27.62,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}于是 他们做出了一个有四台维京发动机的一级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:33.20,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}using steel tanks for the hypergolic propellants of nitrogen tetroxide and UDMH.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:33.20,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}使用装有四氧化二氮和偏二甲肼这样的自燃推进剂的钢制储罐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:37.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This would be the first stage of the Ariane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:37.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这将是阿丽亚娜的第一级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:42.75,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}With the propellant tanks full the first stage had a mass of about 160 tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:42.75,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在推进剂储罐装满后 一级的质量约为160吨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:47.50,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's also notable that in addition to the oxidizer and the fuel tanks
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:47.50,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}另外值得注意的是 除了氧化剂和燃料箱外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:51.40,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}there was a smaller toroidal shaped water tank at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:51.40,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在底部有一个较小的环形水箱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:54.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So this is because of the way the Viking engine operates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:54.94,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么这是因为维京发动机的运作方式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:55.82,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}As you probably know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:55.82,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:03:00.76,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}many high performance rocket engines they have a gas generator that powers the turbo pumps
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:03:00.76,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}许多高性能的火箭发动机会有一个气体发生器 为涡轮泵提供动力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:06.26,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}that is they burn some fuel and the oxidizer and use the exhaust gas to power turbines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:06.26,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即它们燃烧一些燃料和氧化剂 并使用废气驱动涡轮机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.61,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}To keep the temperature down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.61,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了降低温度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:13.81,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}the fuel and the oxidizer are mixed in ratios that don't result in complete combustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:13.81,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}燃料和氧化剂的混合比例会导致不完全燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.16,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Usually it's a fuel rich mixture
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.16,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}通常情况下 这会是富燃的混合方式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.53,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and in the case of SpaceX's Merlin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.53,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而在SpaceX的梅林发动机的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:23.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}you can actually see the fuel rich exhaust black exhaust coming out of the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:23.42,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你实际上可以看到富燃的黑色排气从侧面出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:29.08,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The Viking instead uses mixes at a stoichiometric ratio
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:29.08,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}维京发动机使用的混合比是理想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.08,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and it then cools that exhaust down using water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.08,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后它使用水将该废气冷却下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:36.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Not only does this make the exhaust gases cool enough to be used with the turbine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:36.60,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这不仅使废气冷却到足以给涡轮机使用的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:42.20,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}they also take some of those high pressure exhaust gases and use those to repressurize propellant tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:42.20,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们还能从高压废气中提取一些气体 用来重新增压推进剂罐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:46.83,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And you couldn't do that if it was you know say fuel rich exhaust
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:46.83,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果是富燃的废气 你就无法做到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:51.84,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}because putting fuel-rich hypergolic exhaust into a hypergolic oxidizer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:51.84,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为将富燃的自燃燃料废气排入自燃氧化剂中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.78,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}would result in combustion inside the tank which is a really bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.78,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}会导致储罐内部发生燃烧 这会是一个非常糟糕的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:04:00.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The four engines are mounted at the outer edge of the thrust structure on the bottom of the rocket
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:04:00.62,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}四台发动机安装在火箭底部推力结构的外缘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:06.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and they all have single engine gimbals which are slightly easier than having multi-axis gimbals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:06.68,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且发动机都能单向摆动 这比多向摆动要容易一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:13.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but by moving the engines in pairs they are able to provide full three-axis control of the launch vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:13.54,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但通过成对摆动发动机 他们能够对运载火箭进行完全的三轴控制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:17.03,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The second stage also used the Viking engine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:17.03,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}二级也使用了维京发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:22.27,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but there was only one of them with a two-axis gimbal to provide full yaw and pitch control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:22.27,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但只有一台 这台带有两轴矢量摆动 以提供完全的偏航和俯仰控制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:28.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The gas generator exhaust was diverted through auxiliary nozzles to provide roll control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:28.18,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}燃气发生器的废气通过辅助喷嘴引流 以提供滚转控制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:32.96,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}When fully loaded with propellant, the second stage massed about 40 tons
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:32.96,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当满载推进剂时 二级的质量约为40吨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:38.66,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and unlike the first stage its structure and tankage were aluminium rather than steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:38.66,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}与一级不同的是 它的结构和储罐是铝制的而不是钢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:45.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The third stage was a high energy hydrogen oxygen stage powered by an HM7 engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:45.42,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}三级是由HM7发动机驱动的高能氢氧级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:49.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This is a simple gas generator hydrogen oxygen engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:49.54,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是一台简单的气体发生器(循环)氢氧发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:52.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This stage would have over eight tons of propellant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:52.62,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这级将有超过8吨的推进剂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And would boost the payload up into geostationary transfer orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.42,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并会将有效载荷送到地球静止转移轨道(GTO)上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:05:00.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}There was a fourth optional stage for payloads that went to GEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:05:00.90,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有四级可选 用于将有效载荷(直接)送入地球同步轨道(Scott 口胡GTO)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.76,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This was the Mage solid rocket motor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.76,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是Mage固体火箭发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:08.74,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It was just an apogee kick motor to put the payload into a circular orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:08.74,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这只是一个在远地点工作的发动机 能将有效载荷送入圆形轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:16.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The first full-up integrated test of the Ariane 1 was going to be on December 15 1979.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:16.54,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜1号的第一次全面综合试验 将于1979年12月15日进行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:20.83,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It was going to carry a payload of test instruments called CAT-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:20.83,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它将携带被称为CAT-1的测试仪器的有效载荷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:25.56,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They were stacked and on December 15th they counted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:25.56,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在12月15日 火箭被堆叠起来 并进行倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:30.96,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The engines ignited and 10 seconds later the computer shut down the engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:30.96,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}发动机点火 10秒钟后 电脑关闭了发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.03,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Because it wasn't sure the rocket was going to be able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.03,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为它不确定火箭是否能飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:37.50,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It never left the pad and the engineers spent the next week
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:37.50,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它一直没有离开过发射台 而工程师们在接下来的一周里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:40.49,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}cleaning the rocket preparing it tracing the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:40.49,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}清洗火箭 准备火箭 追查问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:46.87,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and then on December 23rd they were ready to launch again and the weather wasn't cooperative
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:46.87,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后在12月23日 他们准备再次发射 但天气并不配合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:51.48,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but on December 24th the first Ariane one took off
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:51.48,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但在12月24日 第一枚阿丽亚娜1号火箭起飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:55.56,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and successfully placed the satellite into its target orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:55.56,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并成功地将卫星送入其目标轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:06:00.24,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The second launch would unfortunately be destroyed by pogo oscillations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:06:00.24,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}遗憾的是 第二次发射将因纵向藕合振动而被摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:05.81,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The third launch was the first one to geostationary orbit using the Mage apogee booster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:05.81,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}第三次发射会使用Mage远地点火箭 并首次进入地球静止轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:11.95,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}In total there would be 11 launches of this launch vehicle with two of them being failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:11.95,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这种运载火箭总共进行了11次发射 其中两次失败
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.74,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Orobably its most famous payload was the Giotto spacecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.74,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其最著名的有效载荷是乔托号探测器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:19.70,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which made the closest approach to Halley's comet of any spacecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:19.70,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它是所有航天器中最接近哈雷彗星的航天器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:25.93,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and it flew right up until 1986 by which time it had been replaced by the Ariane 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:25.93,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而阿丽亚娜1号一直飞到1986年才被阿丽亚娜3号取代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.85,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What happened to the Ariane 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.85,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么阿丽亚娜2号后来怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.69,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Well actually the Ariane 2 flew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.69,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其实阿丽亚娜2号曾经飞过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:32.53,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It just started flying later than the Ariane 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:32.53,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是比阿丽亚娜3号晚了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:38.70,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So Ariane 2 and 3 were developed in parallel as improved versions of the Ariane 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:38.70,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么阿丽亚娜2号和3号是作为阿丽亚娜1号的改进版同时开发的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:43.26,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}These changes were designed to make it more appealing to the commercial launch market.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:43.26,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这些变化的目的是为了让它对商业发射市场更有吸引力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.41,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}In the late 1970s when they were designing this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.41,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在20世纪70年代末 当他们在设计阿丽亚娜火箭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:52.40,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}the rides to geostationary orbit were the Delta that could put about 1200 kilograms into GTO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:52.40,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能发射到GEO的火箭是德尔塔火箭 可以把大约1200公斤的重量送入GTO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:58.39,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and the Atlas-Centaur who was which was roughly comparable to the Ariane 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:58.39,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而宇宙神-半人马座火箭 与阿丽亚娜1号(的运力)大致相当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:03.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The Ariane 1 found itself more expensive than the Delta but a lot cheaper than the Atlas-Centaur
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:03.94,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而阿丽亚娜1号比德尔塔贵 但比宇宙神-半人马便宜很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:08.36,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but most of the market were looking for payloads that could fly on the Delta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:08.36,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但市场上大多数人都在寻找可以在德尔塔上飞行的有效载荷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:13.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}so the plan was to extend the payload capability of the Ariane
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:13.90,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么计划是扩大阿丽亚娜的有效载荷运力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:17.43,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and put two spacecraft on a single launch vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:17.43,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并能进行一箭双星任务的发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.14,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So they needed to get more performance from their existing vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.14,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以他们需要从现有的运载火箭上获得更多的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.03,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What did they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.03,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那他们做了什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.41,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The first thing they did was they changed the fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.41,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们做的第一件事就是改变燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:28.02,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The Ariane 1 used pure UDMH.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:28.02,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜1号使用的是纯偏二甲肼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:32.09,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They started adding about 25 percent hydrazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:32.09,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}(于是)他们开始添加25%的肼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.76,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The hydrazine is less stable but it provides better specific impulse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.76,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}肼的稳定性较差 但能提供更好的比冲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:40.14,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and so they got about an extra 10 percent chamber pressure out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:40.14,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以燃烧室增加了10%的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:46.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They added two solid propellant boosters which each had a thrust of about 60 tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:46.18,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们加装了两个固体推进剂助推器 每个助推器的推力约为60吨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.75,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Those would be on the Ariane 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.75,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这些将被安装在阿丽亚娜3号上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The Ariane 2 would not need these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.90,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜2号不需要这些助推器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:57.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And the third stage had the tank stretched so that it could carry 10 tons of propellant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:57.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而三级的储箱被拉长了 所以它可以携带10吨的推进剂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:08:04.39,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}With all these changes the Ariane 3 was able to launch two 1200 kilogram satellites in a single launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:08:04.39,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}通过这些改变 阿丽亚娜3号能够在一次发射中发射两颗1200公斤的卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.52,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Inside the payload fairing there would be a structure called the Sylda
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.52,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在有效载荷整流罩内会有一个叫做Sylda的结构
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:14.48,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which was like a carbon fiber shell that would support the top satellite and enclose the lower satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:14.48,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它差不多是一个碳纤维外壳 会支撑顶部的卫星并包围下部的卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}By putting two payloads on a single launch
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.31,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}通过一次发射两个有效载荷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:21.48,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}that allowed them to significantly cut their costs for all the ground operations
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:21.48,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能使他们大幅削减所有地面操作的成本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:25.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}since they're only launching one rocket they're getting two payloads and two customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:25.90,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为只发射一枚火箭就搭载了两个客户的两个有效载荷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:31.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So Arianespace was able to make big moves in the commercial market
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:31.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以阿丽亚娜空间能够在商业市场上有大的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:36.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but the market didn't stay still and bigger and better capabilities were desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:36.94,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但市场并没有停滞不前 而人们希望有更大更好的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:41.82,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ariane 2 only flew 6 times and Ariane 3 only flew 11 times
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:41.82,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜2号只飞了6次 而阿丽亚娜3号只飞了11次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and Ariane 4 would replace both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.94,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而阿丽亚娜4号将取代这两枚运载火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:50.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ariane 4's goal was to launch 4300 kilograms worth of satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:50.42,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜4号的目标是发射总重4300公斤的有效载荷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It was still able to launch two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.42,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它仍能够发射两颗卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:57.07,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The way it did this was the first stage tankage was increased in size
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:57.07,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}增加运力的方法是一级储箱被拉长了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:01.79,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}so that was able to carry about 230 tons of propellant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:01.79,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样就能携带约230吨的推进剂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:08.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The water tank was moved up the rocket into the intertank region between the oxidizer and propellant tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:08.86,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而火箭上的水箱上移到了氧化剂储箱和燃料储箱之间的箱间段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.72,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The second and third stages were identical
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.72,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}二级和三级和之前是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:16.38,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but what Ariane 4 added was up to four external boosters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:16.38,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但阿丽亚娜4号可以捆绑多达四个外部助推器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:22.17,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And these could either be solid propellant or liquid propellant depending upon mission requirements.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:22.17,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}根据任务要求 这些助推器可以是固体推进剂的 也可以是液体推进剂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:29.10,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The bare core with no boosters was rated to put 2100 kilograms into geostationary transfer orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:29.10,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有助推器的光杆火箭的地球静止转移轨道运力是2100公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:34.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}If it had four solid rocket motors that would be raised to about 3400 kilograms
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:34.86,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果它有四个固体火箭发动机 就会提高到3400公斤左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:42.61,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and if it had four liquid boosters that would do 4 700 kilograms into geostationary transfer orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:42.61,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果使用四个液体助推器 就可以将4700公斤的重量送入地球静止转移轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.87,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This was the most popular variant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.87,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是最受欢迎的种类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:49.97,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}As of right now the Ariane 4 is the most popular of the Ariane 5 rockets
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:49.97,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}目前阿丽亚娜4号是5种阿丽亚娜火箭中最受欢迎的型号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:53.34,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}having launched 116 times with only three failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:53.34,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}发射了116次 只有三次失败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:57.97,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It continued launching concurrently with the much heavier Ariane 5
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:57.97,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它继续与更重的阿丽亚娜5号同时发射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:04.69,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}until it was eventually retired and the medium launches then moved over to the Soyuz launch vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:04.69,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}直到它最终退役 而中型运载火箭的发射转移到联盟运载火箭上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:10.98,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But as of right now the Ariane 5 is currently active and it is catching up with the Ariane 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:10.98,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是就目前来说 阿丽亚娜5号正在服役 它正在追赶阿丽亚娜4号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:15.78,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It has 106 launches. 101 of those have been successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:15.78,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它已经发射了106次 其中有101次是成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:21.53,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The Ariane 5 is a huge break in the design philosophy compared to the Ariane 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:21.53,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}与阿丽亚娜4号相比 阿丽亚娜5号在设计理念上有很大的突破
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:29.58,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The Ariane 5 design requirements had it launching a pair of three-ton satellites into geostationary transfer orbit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:29.58,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜5号的设计要求是将一对3吨重的卫星发射到地球静止转移轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:36.26,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but it also specified the ability to launch an 18-ton payload into a low earth orbit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:36.26,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但也包括将18吨重的有效载荷发射到低地球轨道的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:39.58,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and this was for the Hermes space plane
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:39.58,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是为赫尔墨斯航天飞机准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:46.58,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which while the Ariane 5 was built with this in mind the space plane never made it to flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:46.58,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然阿丽亚娜5号在建造的时候就考虑到了这一点 但航天飞机却没有飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.78,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Some people have suggested that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.78,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有些人认为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:53.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}the space plane requirements meant the Ariane 5 was way too big for its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:53.60,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对于航天飞机的要求 阿丽亚娜5号(的运力)实在是太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.36,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But the truth is Ariane had always been launching pairs of satellites
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.36,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但事实上 阿丽亚娜5号一直在进行双星任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.40,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}so this just continued that trend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.40,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以 这只是在持续那个趋势
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.92,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and indeed this large payload requirement has meant that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.92,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}事实上 这一庞大的有效载荷要求意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:08.16,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}they have remained the most popular launch vehicle for geostationary spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:08.16,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它们一直是地球静止轨道航天器最受欢迎的运载火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:13.16,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The base design has two very large solid rocket motors
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:13.16,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}基础设计有两个非常大的固体火箭发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:15.19,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}each massing about 300 tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:15.19,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}每个质量约300吨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:21.48,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And a hydrogen oxygen core that fully fueled is about 170 tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:21.48,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而完全加满燃料的氢氧芯级约为170吨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:27.46,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The engine on the core is the Vulcan which is a gas generator hydrogen oxygen engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:27.46,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}芯级上的发动机是火神发动机 是气体发生器(循环)的氢氧发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.20,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}There is a second stage which is hypergolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.20,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}二级使用的是自燃推进剂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.01,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It's powered by the Aestus engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.01,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它由Aestus发动机提供动力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:36.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And it uses monomethylhydrazine and nitrogen tetroxide
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:36.18,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}推进剂使用的是单甲基肼和四氧化二氮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:40.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and the main distinction here over the previous Viking is that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:40.06,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和以前的维京发动机相比 这里的主要区别是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:44.49,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}this engine on this upper stage is restartable so it can be fired multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:44.49,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个上面级发动机是可以重新启动的 所以可以多次点火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The original Ariane was the G variant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.54,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最初的阿丽亚娜5号是G型的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.61,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}They upgraded it a bit to create the G plus
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.61,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们对它进行了一些升级 也就是G+型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:56.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and in 2005 they debuted an Ariane 5 with a cryogenic upper stage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:56.30,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并在2005年首次推出了带有低温上面级的阿丽亚娜5号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:12:03.22,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}using the same HM7B engine that was used to propel the upper stages for the previous generation Arianes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:12:03.22,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}使用与上一代阿丽亚娜4号上面级所使用发动机相同的HM7B发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:10.23,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}With this upper stage it was now able to put a 10.8 tonnes into geostationary transfer orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:10.23,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有了这个上面级 它现在能够把一个10.8吨的东西送入地球静止转移轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.91,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's the record they set in 2017.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.91,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是他们在2017年创造的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.56,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It still has plenty of launches lined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.56,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜5号还有很多发射任务在排队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:19.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Notably it's going to launch the James Webb Space Telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:19.18,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}值得注意的是 它将发射詹姆斯-韦伯太空望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:23.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and the Jupiter Icy Moons Explorer in coming years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:23.18,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和未来几年的木星冰月探测器(JUICE)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:30.34,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But at the same time Ariane 6 is in development and could be is launching as soon as next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:30.34,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但与此同时 阿丽亚娜6号正在研制中 最快可能在明年发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:37.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}At one point Ariane 6 was proposed to be almost all solid rocket motors with cryogenic upper stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:37.62,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿丽亚娜6号曾一度被提议几乎完全采用固体火箭发动机和低温上面级
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.54,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But they dialed that back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.54,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但他们又将其调了回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:45.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and now it's much closer to an Ariane 5 with shorter solid rocket motors
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:45.62,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而现在它更接近于一个有着更短的固体火箭发动机的阿丽亚娜5号 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:51.85,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and a larger upper stage using the Vinci engine which is a hydrolox engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:51.85,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以及使用芬奇氢氧发动机的更大的上面级
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:55.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So that's what the future holds for the Ariane rocket family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:55.90,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以这就是阿丽亚娜火箭家族的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.69,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Still going strong after 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.69,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}40年后仍在茁壮成长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:12:59.96,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:12:59.96,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.59,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'm Scott Manley. Fly safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.59,1080P-sgsm-63,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是Scott Manley 切记 注意飞行安全
